- Storage boundaries: `Database.md`
- AI and Agent boundary: `AgentDesign.md`
- Evidence boundaries: `References.md`', 'Source: docs/en/Methodology.md > Methodology > Read More. Status: evidence. Tags: agent, database, algorithm, methodology, ui. Purpose: answer FitLog product-rule, algorithm, database, privacy-boundary, or Agent-boundary questions.', null, array['agent', 'database', 'algorithm', 'methodology', 'ui']::text[], 'evidence', 'c1f265c8caa57f2bc6a4985e20cbf0f7b7352f0e9d11180e911313d32609250d', 'phase5_document_chunks.v2', timezone('utc', now())),
